WEBVTT

00:01.839 --> 00:03.800
<font color="#00ff00">your subjects can be proud of.</font>

00:03.840 --> 00:05.800
<font color="#00ffff">LORD MELBOURNE: When you give your</font>
<font color="#00ffff">heart,</font>

00:05.840 --> 00:08.960
<font color="#00ffff">it will be without hesitation,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but you cannot give it to me.</font>

00:09.000 --> 00:11.320
<font color="#00ffff">I do not see the urgency</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for her to marry.</font>

00:11.360 --> 00:13.800
<font color="#00ffff">'Tis more important, I think,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that she chooses wisely.</font>

00:13.840 --> 00:16.880
<font color="#00ff00">You should know that I've sent for</font>
<font color="#00ff00">my nephew Albert.</font>

00:16.920 --> 00:18.520
<font color="#00ffff">Without the Queen's permission?</font>

00:18.560 --> 00:21.680
I don't want a stupid boy like
Albert, Mama, or anyone else.

