01:35.400 --> 01:36.680
(BARKING)

01:36.720 --> 01:40.360
Dash! Now, stop that.
You're being rude.

01:41.840 --> 01:43.760
You mustn't bark at cousin Albert,

01:43.800 --> 01:47.040
even if he does look quite different
to the last time we saw him.

01:47.080 --> 01:50.320
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry if your dog does not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">recognise me.</font>

01:51.160 --> 01:54.240
<font color="#ffff00">I, on the other hand, had no</font>
<font color="#ffff00">difficulty in recognising you,</font>

01:54.280 --> 01:55.880
<font color="#ffff00">although now I believe</font>

01:55.920 --> 01:58.880
<font color="#ffff00">you're playing the piano</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with...fewer mistakes.</font>

02:00.280 --> 02:02.600
<font color="#00ffff">How magnificent you look,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Cousin Victoria.</font>

02:04.200 --> 02:06.200
<font color="#00ffff">Monarchy clearly agrees with you.</font>

02:08.520 --> 02:12.360
<font color="#00ff00">Ernest. Albert.</font>

02:13.360 --> 02:17.160
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, Drina, are your cousins not</font>
<font color="#00ff00">handsome?</font>

02:17.200 --> 02:19.360
<font color="#00ff00">Such fine Coburg specimens.</font>

02:19.400 --> 02:21.480
Please, Mama. They're not racehorses.

02:21.520 --> 02:24.400
<font color="#00ffff">ERNEST: We were hoping tomorrow</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it might be possible</font>

02:24.440 --> 02:26.160
<font color="#00ffff">to see some of your paintings here.</font>

02:26.200 --> 02:29.920
<font color="#00ffff">Albert has just returned from Italy</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and speaks of nothing but the Old</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Masters.</font>

02:29.960 --> 02:33.360
<font color="#ffff00">I believe, in your collection, there</font>
<font color="#ffff00">are some works by Leonardo da Vinci.</font>

02:34.240 --> 02:37.320
Perhaps there are.
I really don't know.

02:38.160 --> 02:41.960
As to tomorrow, Lord Melbourne and I
have a great deal of business to
attend to.

02:42.000 --> 02:43.760
Don't we, Lord M?

02:43.800 --> 02:45.400
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, yes, Ma'am.</font>

02:45.440 --> 02:49.320
<font color="#00ffff">The dispatches from Afghanistan will</font>
<font color="#00ffff">require your complete attention.</font>

02:52.760 --> 02:54.360
<font color="#ffff00">(IN GERMAN)</font>

03:01.440 --> 03:03.440
<font color="#ffff00">This is a fool's errand.</font>

03:08.960 --> 03:11.840
<font color="#00ffff">Please try to be a bit more gallant,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Albert.</font>

03:11.880 --> 03:13.880
<font color="#00ffff">When you take her hand to kiss it,</font>

03:13.920 --> 03:16.000
<font color="#00ffff">you must look deep into her eyes,</font>

03:16.040 --> 03:18.720
<font color="#00ffff">as if you are going to drown</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in them, like this.</font>

03:19.520 --> 03:23.200
<font color="#ffff00">You know, I will never be able</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to match your skill in this area,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ernst.</font>

03:23.240 --> 03:25.360
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps you should marry her,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">instead of me.</font>

03:25.400 --> 03:28.920
<font color="#00ffff">Well, she is exactly my type:</font>
<font color="#00ffff">small and with...</font>

03:28.960 --> 03:31.520
<font color="#00ff00">Every woman is your type, Ernst.</font>

03:31.560 --> 03:34.560
<font color="#00ff00">But you will have to find</font>
<font color="#00ff00">someone else.</font>

03:34.600 --> 03:37.080
<font color="#00ff00">It is Albert's destiny to marry</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Victoria.</font>

03:37.120 --> 03:39.240
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not sure Victoria agrees.</font>

03:39.800 --> 03:42.080
<font color="#ffff00">And she is the one</font>
<font color="#ffff00">who has to propose.</font>

03:42.120 --> 03:43.720
<font color="#00ff00">And she will.</font>

03:43.760 --> 03:48.400
<font color="#00ff00">But she likes men who are attentive,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">like her Lord Melbourne.</font>

03:48.440 --> 03:50.360
<font color="#ffff00">If my manners are not suitable,</font>

03:50.400 --> 03:52.560
<font color="#ffff00">then perhaps I should return</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Coburg.</font>

03:52.600 --> 03:55.440
<font color="#00ff00">If you go home now,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">people will say she has rejected you</font>

03:55.480 --> 03:58.720
<font color="#00ff00">but, if you stay,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you could be King of England.</font>

03:59.640 --> 04:01.080
<font color="#ffff00">No, Uncle.</font>

04:02.400 --> 04:04.800
<font color="#ffff00">I would be the Queen of England's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">husband.</font>

04:05.560 --> 04:07.640
VICTORIA:
Did you see the way he looked at me?

04:07.680 --> 04:10.640
As if I were a child
who hadn't done her lessons.

04:10.680 --> 04:13.880
<font color="#00ff00">He is a younger son from nowhere...</font>

04:14.600 --> 04:16.760
<font color="#00ff00">..and you are a queen.</font>

04:27.520 --> 04:29.120
Do you think the Prince handsome?

04:29.160 --> 04:31.920
<font color="#00ffff">It's not for me to say, Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">But I am asking you.</font>

04:34.680 --> 04:37.680
<font color="#00ffff">Then, yes,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Prince is very handsome.</font>

04:39.280 --> 04:40.880
But he never smiles.

04:42.520 --> 04:44.520
I wonder if he can.

05:00.040 --> 05:02.240
<font color="#00ffff">MAN: Clear off! Not round here!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">No more.</font>

05:12.720 --> 05:17.240
<font color="#00ff00">Good morning. I would like</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to introduce Herr Lohlein,</font>

05:17.280 --> 05:20.000
<font color="#00ff00">who is valet</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to Prince Ernest and Prince Albert.</font>

05:20.040 --> 05:22.040
<font color="#00ffff">(IN GERMAN)</font>

05:22.080 --> 05:25.440
<font color="#ffff00">We speak English in this part</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the palace, Mr Lohlein.</font>

05:26.480 --> 05:28.480
<font color="#00ff00">(IN GERMAN)</font>

05:35.400 --> 05:37.720
How small they are!

05:38.440 --> 05:42.040
<font color="#00ff00">One of these, Ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is sufficient to carry a letter...</font>

05:47.400 --> 05:52.760
<font color="#00ff00">..is sufficient to carry a letter</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to Brighton or to the Isle of Bute.</font>

05:52.800 --> 05:55.000
But how will the little pictures
stay affixed?

05:55.040 --> 05:58.800
<font color="#00ff00">The stamps, Ma'am, have a layer</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of gum arabic on the back.</font>

06:01.840 --> 06:04.160
So, everybody who wants to send
a letter...

06:05.880 --> 06:07.400
..will have to lick my face?

06:07.440 --> 06:09.360
<font color="#00ff00">Precisely, Ma'am,</font>

06:09.400 --> 06:13.720
<font color="#00ff00">though those of a more genteel</font>
<font color="#00ff00">nature may use a little brush.</font>

06:15.960 --> 06:18.000
(LAUGHTER)

06:24.640 --> 06:27.400
Do you think Cousin Albert
disapproves of us, Dash?

06:28.320 --> 06:30.560
(CHUCKLES)

06:30.600 --> 06:34.040
<font color="#ffff00">Forgive me. I thought you were</font>
<font color="#ffff00">addressing your dog.</font>

06:34.080 --> 06:36.360
<font color="#ffff00">I think this is a remarkable</font>
<font color="#ffff00">invention,</font>

06:36.400 --> 06:41.160
<font color="#ffff00">so I find nothing to laugh at...</font>
<font color="#ffff00">only to admire.</font>

06:45.400 --> 06:50.720
Oh! I am so vexed, I could scream!
<font color="#00ffff">I wouldn't worry.</font>

06:50.760 --> 06:53.560
<font color="#00ffff">Latest reports say our forces have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">defeated Dost Mohammad.</font>

06:53.600 --> 06:56.200
<font color="#00ffff">We'll be in Kabul in weeks.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I was talking about my cousin.</font>

06:56.240 --> 06:58.560
<font color="#00ffff">Oh. Which cousin would that be?</font>

06:58.600 --> 07:00.600
Albert, of course.

07:01.400 --> 07:04.160
He's such a...prig.

07:05.280 --> 07:07.760
<font color="#00ffff">You do not see him as a possible</font>
<font color="#00ffff">husband, then?</font>

07:07.800 --> 07:09.720
I would rather marry Robert Peel.

07:11.120 --> 07:13.880
<font color="#00ffff">I wonder what Lady Peel</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would say to that.</font>

07:15.160 --> 07:16.240
(CHUCKLES)

07:25.880 --> 07:27.600
<font color="#00ff00">Aren't you going to bring me inside?</font>

07:27.640 --> 07:29.680
<font color="#00ffff">You know that's not a good idea.</font>

07:29.720 --> 07:31.360
<font color="#00ff00">Mrs Collins put my rent up</font>
<font color="#00ff00">last week.</font>

07:31.400 --> 07:33.600
<font color="#00ff00">I can't manage any more</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on what you give me.</font>

07:33.640 --> 07:35.480
<font color="#00ffff">I don't get paid till Michaelmas.</font>

07:38.720 --> 07:40.720
<font color="#00ff00">I'm sure you'll think of something.</font>

07:42.120 --> 07:44.400
<font color="#00ff00">A resourceful girl like you.</font>

07:44.440 --> 07:47.120
<font color="#00ff00">I'm sure a palace is full</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of trifles no-one would miss.</font>

07:47.160 --> 07:48.760
<font color="#00ffff">I'm no thief.</font>

07:48.800 --> 07:51.520
<font color="#00ff00">And you're no Eliza Skerrett,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">neither. </font><font color="#00ffff"> Ssh!</font>

08:00.080 --> 08:01.880
(BELL CHIMING)

08:05.880 --> 08:07.880
(CHILDREN CHATTER)

08:17.680 --> 08:19.200
<font color="#ffff00">It's remarkable.</font>

08:19.240 --> 08:21.560
<font color="#ffff00">A way of reproducing nature</font>
<font color="#ffff00">quite faithfully.</font>

08:21.600 --> 08:26.720
<font color="#00ffff">Look at that wart. I'm not sure</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I would like to be reproduced</font>
<font color="#00ffff">quite that faithfully.</font>

08:26.760 --> 08:29.520
<font color="#ffff00">Do you not want to see yourself</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as you appear to others?</font>

08:29.560 --> 08:31.520
<font color="#00ffff">Nein.</font>

08:31.560 --> 08:35.679
<font color="#00ff00">No! Go away. Go away. No.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Please...</font>

08:38.480 --> 08:43.440
<font color="#00ff00">Buy a match, sir. Buy a match, sir.</font>

08:43.480 --> 08:45.280
<font color="#ffff00">Lohlein...</font>

08:48.760 --> 08:50.440
<font color="#ffff00">(WHISPERS)</font>

08:50.480 --> 08:52.440
<font color="#00ff00">Buy a match, sir.</font>

08:54.040 --> 08:55.640
(COIN DROPS IN BOX)

08:55.680 --> 08:57.960
<font color="#00ff00">Thank you, sir.</font>

08:58.000 --> 09:00.000
(CLINK OF CUTLERY)

09:01.840 --> 09:03.840
(DOG BARKS)

09:07.480 --> 09:10.320
VICTORIA:
I hope you enjoyed your day.

09:10.360 --> 09:12.560
Lord M and I have been so busy
with the Army Lists.

09:12.600 --> 09:17.440
<font color="#00ffff">Albert and I visited the National</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Gallery. We are quite the tourists.</font>

09:27.480 --> 09:31.200
<font color="#ffff00">I have not yet finished.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">But the Queen has, Your Highness.</font>

09:32.480 --> 09:35.320
VICTORIA: Oh, did you see
my portrait? The one by Hayter.

09:35.360 --> 09:37.360
I think it is my favourite.

09:38.640 --> 09:40.960
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

09:41.000 --> 09:43.080
<font color="#ffff00">We went to look at the Old Masters.</font>

09:44.160 --> 09:45.840
<font color="#ffff00">There is a very fine Rubens.</font>

09:45.880 --> 09:47.320
(DOG WHINES)

09:48.760 --> 09:50.760
I don't care for Rubens at all.

09:51.560 --> 09:53.160
All that wobbling flesh.

10:08.480 --> 10:10.840
<font color="#ffff00">ALBERT: Lord Melbourne.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Oh.</font>

10:10.880 --> 10:13.640
<font color="#ffff00">I should very much like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to visit your Parliament.</font>

10:13.680 --> 10:16.640
<font color="#ffff00">We have nothing like this at home.</font>

10:16.680 --> 10:18.880
<font color="#00ffff">You'd be most welcome, sir.</font>

10:18.920 --> 10:21.880
<font color="#00ffff">I would suggest you might</font>
<font color="#00ffff">want to go incognito.</font>

10:21.920 --> 10:24.880
<font color="#ffff00">Why's that?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Well, there are some MPs,</font>

10:24.920 --> 10:27.560
<font color="#00ffff">Tories mainly,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">who might not like to feel</font>

10:27.600 --> 10:30.440
<font color="#00ffff">they were being inspected</font>
<font color="#00ffff">by a German prince.</font>

10:32.000 --> 10:35.960
<font color="#ffff00">I see. What about you,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Melbourne?</font>

10:37.000 --> 10:39.000
<font color="#00ffff">What do I think?</font>

10:40.000 --> 10:41.600
<font color="#00ffff">I think we should join the ladies.</font>

10:42.600 --> 10:44.800
(MURMUR OF CONVERSATION)

10:47.880 --> 10:50.040
Lord M,
you must come and play with me.

10:50.080 --> 10:51.960
I feel sure you will bring me luck.

10:52.000 --> 10:56.080
<font color="#00ffff">Pleasure, Ma'am. Perhaps we could</font>
<font color="#00ffff">bring up another table, so the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Princes can play, too.</font>

10:56.120 --> 10:59.680
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, no, no. Please, there's no need.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I do not care to play card games.</font>

11:02.800 --> 11:04.800
<font color="#00ffff">But I do. May I join the game?</font>

11:05.880 --> 11:09.440
<font color="#ffff00">(IN GERMAN)</font>

11:11.360 --> 11:13.360
<font color="#00ff00">(DUBIOUSLY) Yes.</font>

11:13.400 --> 11:15.320
(MELLOW PIANO MUSIC)

11:34.080 --> 11:39.640
<font color="#00ffff">ERNEST: Cousin Victoria, will you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">do me the very great honour of</font>
<font color="#00ffff">playing for me?</font>

11:40.960 --> 11:42.160
The piano is in use.

11:42.200 --> 11:46.360
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, but I feel that tonight cannot</font>
<font color="#00ffff">be complete without a Schubert duet.</font>

11:46.400 --> 11:48.840
<font color="#00ff00">And the Queen and her cousin</font>
<font color="#00ff00">both play so well.</font>

11:53.840 --> 11:57.200
(PIANO CONTINUES)
<font color="#00ffff">ERNEST: I adore Schubert.</font>

12:00.360 --> 12:02.520
(STOPS PLAYING)

12:03.800 --> 12:07.600
<font color="#ffff00">My apologies.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I did not know you wanted to play.</font>

12:10.080 --> 12:12.960
Ernest has requested a duet.
Schubert.

12:15.840 --> 12:17.720
I believe there is some music here.

12:18.680 --> 12:22.200
<font color="#ffff00">ALBERT: Oh, yes. I know this.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Which part do you prefer?</font>

12:22.240 --> 12:24.800
<font color="#ffff00">I believe the primo part is more</font>
<font color="#ffff00">difficult.</font>

12:24.840 --> 12:27.600
I have never had a problem with it.
<font color="#ffff00">No?</font>

12:28.520 --> 12:32.720
<font color="#ffff00">But it has so many chords,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and you have such...small hands.</font>

12:36.800 --> 12:38.600
Ready?

12:39.480 --> 12:41.480
One, two, three...

12:51.720 --> 12:53.480
Am I going too fast for you, Albert?

12:53.520 --> 12:55.640
<font color="#ffff00">I believe you're going too fast for</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Schubert.</font>

12:55.680 --> 12:57.880
<font color="#ffff00">But if that is the pace you wish to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">play it at...</font>

12:57.920 --> 12:59.920
(BOTH RESUME PLAYING)

13:25.880 --> 13:27.560
(CONCLUDING CHORDS)

13:33.160 --> 13:34.240
<font color="#00ff00">WOMAN: Bravo!</font>

13:36.040 --> 13:38.040
<font color="#ffff00">You play very well, Cousin.</font>

13:41.640 --> 13:44.320
<font color="#ffff00">But I believe you do not practise</font>
<font color="#ffff00">enough.</font>

13:44.360 --> 13:48.200
<font color="#ffff00">It is necessary to play</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for at least one hour each day.</font>

13:49.560 --> 13:52.200
A queen does not have time
for scales every day.

13:52.240 --> 13:54.240
<font color="#ffff00">Only for card games.</font>

14:06.920 --> 14:08.920
(SHE PRACTISES SCALES)

14:19.760 --> 14:22.200
<font color="#00ff00">So, Victoria...</font>

14:22.240 --> 14:26.120
<font color="#00ff00">Normally, it is the man</font>
<font color="#00ff00">who must declare his love,</font>

14:26.160 --> 14:31.160
<font color="#00ff00">but, in your case, you will have to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">overcome your maidenly modesty</font>

14:31.200 --> 14:32.800
<font color="#00ff00">and propose to Albert.</font>

14:32.840 --> 14:35.240
I'm sorry, Uncle,
but Albert and I are not suited.

14:35.280 --> 14:37.560
He has no manners.

14:37.600 --> 14:40.640
Yesterday, he was playing
my keyboard as if he owned it.

14:51.320 --> 14:53.320
<font color="#00ffff">(IN GERMAN)</font>

14:59.200 --> 15:02.920
<font color="#ffff00">English, please.</font>

15:02.960 --> 15:04.960
<font color="#ffff00">Only English.</font>

15:05.000 --> 15:08.080
<font color="#00ffff">Last night, we went to a very</font>
<font color="#00ffff">interesting establishment,</font>

15:08.120 --> 15:10.040
<font color="#00ffff">called a nunnery,</font>

15:10.080 --> 15:12.960
<font color="#00ffff">but I saw no nuns there.</font>

15:13.000 --> 15:15.720
<font color="#ffff00">I wish you would be more prudent,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Ernst.</font>

15:16.560 --> 15:18.200
<font color="#ffff00">It's hard enough with Papa.</font>

15:18.240 --> 15:21.840
<font color="#00ffff">But the girls here</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are too delicious.</font>

15:21.880 --> 15:23.880
<font color="#00ffff">So, the sooner that you marry</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Victoria,</font>

15:23.920 --> 15:25.760
<font color="#00ffff">the faster I can go back to Coburg,</font>

15:25.800 --> 15:28.040
<font color="#00ffff">where there are no more</font>
<font color="#00ffff">distractions.</font>

15:28.080 --> 15:30.080
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria is impossible.</font>

15:30.760 --> 15:34.400
<font color="#ffff00">She seems to spend more time with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">her lapdog than her own mother.</font>

15:34.440 --> 15:36.200
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, what does that matter?</font>

15:36.240 --> 15:37.960
<font color="#00ffff">I saw you at the piano.</font>

15:38.000 --> 15:40.560
<font color="#00ffff">It seemed to me that you played</font>
<font color="#00ffff">together rather well.</font>

15:41.200 --> 15:43.760
<font color="#00ffff">And did you have to touch her quite</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so often?</font>

15:45.880 --> 15:48.480
<font color="#ffff00">It was a complicated piece.</font>

15:50.120 --> 15:51.720
<font color="#00ffff">Ja.</font>

15:53.480 --> 15:55.080
<font color="#00ffff">Cousin Victoria.</font>

15:55.120 --> 15:58.920
<font color="#00ffff">Good morning.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You look radiant in the sunshine.</font>

15:58.960 --> 16:02.720
<font color="#00ffff">Duchess, may I talk to you a moment</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about my theory...</font>

16:04.800 --> 16:06.400
Do you like gardens, Albert?

16:09.560 --> 16:11.560
<font color="#ffff00">I prefer forests.</font>

16:13.480 --> 16:16.640
But this is the largest private
garden in London.

16:16.680 --> 16:20.880
<font color="#ffff00">To be among the trees when the wind</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is blowing is to feel the sublime.</font>

16:22.520 --> 16:25.600
Well, if you like trees so much,
you should go to Windsor.

16:25.640 --> 16:27.560
There are plenty of trees there.

16:29.040 --> 16:32.520
<font color="#ffff00">But I can only go there</font>
<font color="#ffff00">if you invite me, Cousin.</font>

16:39.560 --> 16:43.920
<font color="#ffff00">Aunt, I had no idea you had such</font>
<font color="#ffff00">talent.</font>

16:45.320 --> 16:49.400
<font color="#ffff00">May I suggest some shading here,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to balance the composition?</font>

16:51.040 --> 16:53.040
<font color="#00ff00">DUCHESS: Thank you, Albert.</font>

17:13.839 --> 17:15.640
(FOOTSTEPS)

17:17.520 --> 17:20.560
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, the price of whalebone these</font>
<font color="#00ff00">days is shocking. Shocking!</font>

17:23.040 --> 17:25.040
I didn't take you for a flatterer.

17:28.040 --> 17:30.280
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I try not to say things</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I do not mean,</font>

17:30.320 --> 17:33.560
<font color="#ffff00">but I also try to be kind,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">where possible.</font>

17:35.880 --> 17:37.880
And you think Mama needs kindness?

17:40.680 --> 17:42.680
<font color="#ffff00">Don't you?</font>

17:44.840 --> 17:47.240
<font color="#ffff00">I have seen the way</font>
<font color="#ffff00">she looks at you, Victoria.</font>

17:49.080 --> 17:52.480
<font color="#ffff00">She loves you very much.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">You don't know anything about it.</font>

17:53.760 --> 17:56.680
<font color="#ffff00">No. No. That's... That's true.</font>

17:59.920 --> 18:02.840
<font color="#ffff00">But I do know what it is like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">not to have a mother.</font>

18:11.960 --> 18:14.280
<font color="#ffff00">PENGE: Red-topped boots, indeed!</font>

18:15.120 --> 18:18.480
<font color="#ffff00">Why can't they use black or brown,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like everyone else?</font>

18:18.520 --> 18:21.440
<font color="#00ff00">That's not Herr Lohlein's fault,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is it, Mr Penge?</font>

18:23.960 --> 18:25.040
<font color="#00ffff">Baroness...</font>

18:28.720 --> 18:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">There is to be dancing tonight,</font>

18:30.560 --> 18:34.000
<font color="#ffff00">so the Queen will want the white</font>
<font color="#ffff00">muslin and flowers for her hair.</font>

18:34.040 --> 18:35.800
<font color="#00ff00">Very good, Baroness.</font>

18:39.360 --> 18:41.360
<font color="#ffff00">(IN GERMAN)</font>

19:00.800 --> 19:01.880
(DOOR CLOSES)

19:01.920 --> 19:04.080
We will expect you for dinner
tonight.

19:04.120 --> 19:06.120
There will be dancing afterwards.

19:06.160 --> 19:07.600
Nothing elaborate.

19:07.640 --> 19:10.720
<font color="#00ffff">I thought you weren't having any</font>
<font color="#00ffff">more balls. </font><font color="#ffffff"> Oh, no, it isn't a ball.</font>

19:10.760 --> 19:12.680
Just a very small dance.

19:12.720 --> 19:15.200
I must do something to entertain the
Princes.

19:16.080 --> 19:17.720
<font color="#00ffff">I seem to remember you telling me</font>

19:17.760 --> 19:20.000
<font color="#00ffff">that Prince Albert</font>
<font color="#00ffff">does not care for dancing.</font>

19:20.040 --> 19:22.240
Oh, I wouldn't want to dance with
him, anyway.

19:22.280 --> 19:24.120
It would be like waltzing with a
poker.

19:24.160 --> 19:26.800
<font color="#00ffff">I thought you might prefer the blue</font>
<font color="#00ffff">silk.</font>

19:26.840 --> 19:28.680
The blue silk, definitely.

19:28.720 --> 19:31.640
The Baroness always likes
to dress me like a little girl.

19:31.680 --> 19:34.320
<font color="#00ffff">Might I suggest we add some</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of the diamond pins?</font>

19:34.360 --> 19:36.360
<font color="#00ffff">It will look more elegant.</font>

19:36.400 --> 19:38.160
More elegant?

19:39.240 --> 19:40.800
Yes, indeed.

19:41.880 --> 19:44.880
<font color="#00ff00">BRODIE: With Lord Melbourne's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">compliments, Ma'am.</font>

20:01.680 --> 20:03.680
(STRINGS PLAYING A LIGHT DANCE TUNE)

20:13.840 --> 20:16.320
VICTORIA: How do you like
our English dances, Ernest?

20:17.040 --> 20:19.320
<font color="#00ffff">I like your Gay Gordons very much,</font>

20:19.360 --> 20:22.000
<font color="#00ffff">but nothing compares to a waltz.</font>

20:22.040 --> 20:25.280
<font color="#00ffff">Should they play a waltz, you must</font>
<font color="#00ffff">dance with my brother Albert.</font>

20:25.320 --> 20:27.160
<font color="#00ffff">He would benefit greatly</font>

20:27.200 --> 20:29.520
<font color="#00ffff">from a lesson from someone</font>
<font color="#00ffff">as graceful as you.</font>

20:30.560 --> 20:33.680
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen seems to enjoy dancing</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with Prince Ernest...</font>

20:34.320 --> 20:36.720
<font color="#00ff00">..whom I find most charming.</font>

20:36.760 --> 20:39.040
<font color="#00ff00">One might even forget he was German.</font>

20:39.080 --> 20:40.160
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

20:40.200 --> 20:42.200
<font color="#00ff00">EMMA: Unlike his brother.</font>

20:43.080 --> 20:45.160
<font color="#00ff00">So stiff and awkward.</font>

20:45.200 --> 20:47.200
<font color="#00ffff">A clockwork prince.</font>

20:50.040 --> 20:52.280
<font color="#00ff00">EMMA: Look how he's gazing at her.</font>

20:52.320 --> 20:54.280
<font color="#00ffff">MELBOURNE:</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, but what's he looking at?</font>

20:54.920 --> 20:56.680
<font color="#00ffff">A woman?</font>

20:56.720 --> 20:59.200
<font color="#00ffff">Or the most eligible match</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in Europe?</font>

21:00.720 --> 21:02.000
(MUSIC FINISHES)

21:02.040 --> 21:03.320
(SIGHS)

21:03.360 --> 21:05.760
<font color="#00ffff">ERNEST: Your Majesty. Vielen Dank.</font>

21:05.800 --> 21:07.800
(APPLAUSE)

21:09.040 --> 21:12.240
<font color="#00ffff">Albert, they are going to play a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">waltz.</font>

21:14.800 --> 21:17.720
<font color="#ffff00">I think she would rather dance</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with Lord Melbourne.</font>

21:18.360 --> 21:19.920
<font color="#00ffff">ERNEST: Nonsense.</font>

21:20.600 --> 21:23.200
Oh...dear Lord M!

21:24.240 --> 21:27.560
Thank you for the flowers.
They're as beautiful as ever.

21:27.600 --> 21:30.360
<font color="#00ffff">The glasshouses of Brocket Hall</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are at your service, Ma'am.</font>

21:31.400 --> 21:33.600
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps I could have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the pleasure of...</font>

21:37.160 --> 21:39.480
<font color="#00ffff">..of seeing you wear them.</font>

21:39.520 --> 21:41.840
<font color="#ffff00">May I have the pleasure?</font>

22:16.280 --> 22:18.280
You dance beautifully.

22:19.200 --> 22:21.720
<font color="#ffff00">I think, before that, I was afraid.</font>

22:22.760 --> 22:24.360
Afraid?

22:25.240 --> 22:27.240
<font color="#ffff00">Of appearing ridiculous.</font>

22:27.880 --> 22:31.200
<font color="#ffff00">It's hard sometimes to find the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">rhythm.</font>

22:33.520 --> 22:35.000
<font color="#ffff00">Not with you.</font>

23:07.240 --> 23:09.240
<font color="#ffff00">Forgive me.</font>

23:09.280 --> 23:11.280
<font color="#ffff00">Your corsage.</font>

23:12.280 --> 23:14.840
<font color="#ffff00">My mother always used to come in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and kiss me good night</font>

23:14.880 --> 23:16.560
<font color="#ffff00">before she went to parties.</font>

23:16.600 --> 23:19.520
<font color="#ffff00">She would always wear those flowers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in her hair.</font>

23:22.720 --> 23:24.720
Then you must have this.

23:28.720 --> 23:30.720
To remind you of your mother.

23:31.960 --> 23:33.960
<font color="#ffff00">But I have no place...</font>

23:50.600 --> 23:52.600
<font color="#ffff00">I will hold them here.</font>

23:54.440 --> 23:56.440
<font color="#ffff00">Next to my heart.</font>

24:05.160 --> 24:06.560
(APPLAUSE)

24:26.480 --> 24:28.040
(BIRDSONG)

24:28.080 --> 24:29.760
(DOOR OPENS)

24:29.800 --> 24:33.640
<font color="#00ff00">Good morning, Majesty.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I trust you slept well.</font>

24:34.720 --> 24:36.680
Very well.

24:39.000 --> 24:41.000
I have decided to go to Windsor.

24:41.560 --> 24:43.440
<font color="#00ff00">Windsor?</font>

24:43.480 --> 24:45.320
<font color="#00ff00">But you don't like Windsor.</font>

24:45.360 --> 24:47.120
Of course I like Windsor.

24:47.160 --> 24:49.000
<font color="#00ff00">When do you want to go?</font>

24:49.040 --> 24:52.320
Immediately.
Please make all the arrangements.

24:52.360 --> 24:55.840
<font color="#00ff00">Is everyone to come, Majesty?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Even the Princes?</font>

24:56.960 --> 25:00.720
Now, Lehzen, are you suggesting
that we leave them behind?

25:00.760 --> 25:01.880
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

25:01.920 --> 25:03.840
(HUMS)
<font color="#00ff00">(GASPS)</font>

25:09.720 --> 25:11.040
<font color="#00ffff">(IN GERMAN)</font>

25:13.720 --> 25:14.880
<font color="#00ffff">Bleurgh.</font>

25:14.920 --> 25:19.600
<font color="#00ff00">There won't be time to be making</font>
<font color="#00ff00">special meals for Prince Albert.</font>

25:20.680 --> 25:24.400
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen has decided to go to</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Windsor. Immediately.</font>

25:24.440 --> 25:26.440
<font color="#00ffff">Windsor on a Wednesday.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Whatever next?</font>

25:26.480 --> 25:29.240
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you heard</font>
<font color="#ffff00">what the Baroness said.</font>

25:29.280 --> 25:30.560
<font color="#00ffff">Was ist...Windsor?</font>

25:30.600 --> 25:33.520
<font color="#00ff00">(MIMICKING HIM)</font>
<font color="#00ff00">"Oh...was ist Windsor?"</font>

25:33.560 --> 25:35.560
<font color="#00ffff">(IN GERMAN)</font>

25:41.440 --> 25:43.360
<font color="#ffff00">(IN GERMAN)</font>

26:06.160 --> 26:07.240
Lord M!

26:07.280 --> 26:10.600
<font color="#00ffff">I've brought the latest dispatch</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from Macnaghten in Kabul.</font>

26:10.640 --> 26:12.920
But, you see, I have decided
to go to Windsor.

26:12.960 --> 26:15.480
<font color="#00ffff">On a Wednesday?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes.</font>

26:16.720 --> 26:18.800
You know how fond I am of...trees.

26:20.040 --> 26:23.200
<font color="#00ffff">Trees?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Yes. We will expect you for dinner.</font>

26:23.240 --> 26:25.840
<font color="#00ffff">That might be difficult, Ma'am.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I must go to the House.</font>

26:25.880 --> 26:27.480
<font color="#00ffff">You will have much to distract you.</font>

26:27.520 --> 26:30.120
<font color="#00ffff">Prince Albert would like to see</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the Windsor collection.</font>

26:30.160 --> 26:32.400
If we were dining here,
you would come.

26:32.440 --> 26:35.120
I don't see why Windsor should be
any different.

26:37.960 --> 26:41.080
<font color="#00ffff">I'm not doing it, Eliza. I can't.</font>

26:41.120 --> 26:44.880
<font color="#00ffff">If I get caught, we're both sunk.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">And, besides, it ain't right.</font>

26:44.920 --> 26:48.440
<font color="#00ff00">Since when did you know the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">difference between right and wrong?</font>

26:51.480 --> 26:53.040
<font color="#00ffff">Look...</font>

26:53.080 --> 26:57.400
<font color="#00ffff">This should fetch a shilling,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at least. It's the best I can do.</font>

27:04.760 --> 27:06.640
<font color="#00ff00">I expect we won't get there before</font>
<font color="#00ff00">dark.</font>

27:06.680 --> 27:09.640
Stop grumbling, Lehzen.
Think of the forests.

27:21.080 --> 27:25.840
<font color="#00ff00">I wonder why Victoria has developed</font>
<font color="#00ff00">this sudden enthusiasm for Windsor.</font>

27:41.120 --> 27:42.800
(KNOCK AT DOOR)

27:55.000 --> 27:59.920
<font color="#ffff00">For your Serene Highnesses,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with the Queen's compliments.</font>

27:59.960 --> 28:03.920
<font color="#00ffff">Fancy dress?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">The Windsor uniform, Your Highness,</font>

28:03.960 --> 28:09.760
<font color="#ffff00">was designed by George III</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for members of the English court.</font>

28:14.960 --> 28:19.480
<font color="#00ffff">I wonder if King George designed it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">before or after he went mad.</font>

28:25.520 --> 28:27.520
(GASPS)

28:49.040 --> 28:51.560
(CLOCK CHIMING)

28:54.960 --> 28:57.800
<font color="#00ff00">I did not know you were at the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Castle, Lord Melbourne.</font>

28:57.840 --> 29:01.000
<font color="#00ffff">I should be at the House,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">but the Queen was most insistent.</font>

29:01.040 --> 29:03.680
<font color="#00ff00">And you do not care to refuse her?</font>

29:05.880 --> 29:07.600
<font color="#00ffff">She is the Queen, sir.</font>

29:07.640 --> 29:13.560
<font color="#ffff00">Their Serene Highnesses,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Prince Ernest and Prince Albert.</font>

29:13.600 --> 29:16.520
<font color="#00ff00">And in the Windsor uniform!</font>

29:16.560 --> 29:18.360
<font color="#00ff00">How pleasing!</font>

29:26.920 --> 29:28.920
Oh, dear Lord M.

29:29.440 --> 29:31.680
I am so glad you were able to come.

29:31.720 --> 29:33.440
If you'll excuse me.

29:35.320 --> 29:37.000
Ernest, Albert.

29:37.040 --> 29:39.360
How well you look in the uniform.

29:39.400 --> 29:43.240
<font color="#00ffff">Your grandfather certainly spared</font>
<font color="#00ffff">no expense. (CHUCKLES)</font>

29:44.640 --> 29:46.520
And you, Albert...?

29:48.600 --> 29:50.600
<font color="#ffff00">I find the gold braid rather heavy.</font>

29:54.680 --> 29:56.760
Perhaps you'd care to look at
the paintings.

30:06.280 --> 30:08.840
Agatha Bas by Rembrandt,

30:08.880 --> 30:13.320
who's generally considered to be one
of the finest of the Dutch masters.

30:13.360 --> 30:16.040
<font color="#ffff00">The brushwork is exquisite.</font>

30:16.720 --> 30:18.720
<font color="#ffff00">Look at the lace.</font>

30:20.280 --> 30:22.280
It's not very flattering, though.

30:23.200 --> 30:25.000
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps.</font>

30:25.840 --> 30:27.960
<font color="#ffff00">What would you prefer?</font>

30:28.840 --> 30:32.160
<font color="#ffff00">Flattery or...truth?</font>

30:37.240 --> 30:41.680
Tell me, Lord M: have you read
Oliver Twist by Mr Dickens?

30:41.720 --> 30:46.160
<font color="#00ffff">I have no great desire to consort</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with grave-robbers, pickpockets</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and the like.</font>

30:46.200 --> 30:48.240
<font color="#00ffff">Why would I want</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to read about them?</font>

30:48.280 --> 30:51.600
<font color="#ffff00">You know, Lord Melbourne, I believe</font>
<font color="#ffff00">this Dickens that you speak of</font>

30:51.640 --> 30:55.200
<font color="#ffff00">writes most accurately</font>
<font color="#ffff00">about the conditions of the poor.</font>

30:55.240 --> 31:00.520
<font color="#ffff00">Do you...not wish to know the truth</font>
<font color="#ffff00">about the country which you govern?</font>

31:00.560 --> 31:03.800
<font color="#00ffff">As I've been in government for</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ten years, Your Serene Highness,</font>

31:03.840 --> 31:07.120
<font color="#00ffff">I believe</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I'm tolerably well informed.</font>

31:16.520 --> 31:19.600
<font color="#00ffff">Sometimes I find it hard to believe</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that we are brothers.</font>

31:19.640 --> 31:22.040
<font color="#00ffff">Albert is always up before dawn.</font>

31:23.360 --> 31:25.360
You do seem to be very different.

31:25.400 --> 31:28.360
You are so easy, and he is...

31:30.800 --> 31:32.720
Well, he is not.

31:34.120 --> 31:36.120
<font color="#00ffff">Albert is worth ten of me.</font>

31:37.920 --> 31:40.120
(HORSE'S HOOVES POUNDING)

31:42.760 --> 31:45.160
Good morning, Albert.

31:45.200 --> 31:47.720
I do hope you find the park here
more to your taste.

31:48.200 --> 31:52.040
<font color="#ffff00">There is a word we have in German:</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Waldeinsamkeit.</font>

31:52.080 --> 31:55.040
<font color="#ffff00">A feeling of being at one with the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">forest.</font>

31:55.080 --> 31:56.600
<font color="#ffff00">I have it here.</font>

31:56.640 --> 31:58.400
Waldeinsamkeit?

32:01.200 --> 32:04.440
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, I had completely forgotten I'd</font>
<font color="#00ffff">arranged to meet Uncle Leopold.</font>

32:04.480 --> 32:07.680
<font color="#00ffff">Lord Alfred, would you be kind</font>
<font color="#00ffff">enough to show me back to the house?</font>

32:08.400 --> 32:10.000
<font color="#00ff00">ALFRED: With pleasure.</font>

32:10.040 --> 32:13.200
<font color="#00ffff">Shall we make it interesting?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Ten guineas to the first man there.</font>

32:13.240 --> 32:15.240
<font color="#00ffff">You're on!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(HORSE WHINNIES)</font>

32:21.680 --> 32:25.480
There is an oak in there that's been
here since the Norman Conquest.

32:26.160 --> 32:28.160
Would you like to see it?

32:28.960 --> 32:30.520
<font color="#ffff00">Very much.</font>

32:30.560 --> 32:32.720
<font color="#ffff00">Allow me.</font>

32:39.560 --> 32:41.360
<font color="#ffff00">Please...</font>

32:47.440 --> 32:48.760
(BARKING)

33:02.120 --> 33:04.400
(CHUCKLES)

33:07.800 --> 33:10.800
Albert! (LAUGHS)

33:16.480 --> 33:18.200
(CHUCKLES)

33:18.240 --> 33:20.800
<font color="#ffff00">No, no. Don't put it on. Please.</font>

33:20.840 --> 33:23.640
<font color="#ffff00">I like to see you unbound.</font>

33:23.680 --> 33:25.480
<font color="#ffff00">You are not so much a queen.</font>

33:28.320 --> 33:30.320
I think that might be treason.

33:31.880 --> 33:33.120
(LAUGHS)

33:33.880 --> 33:35.680
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, you're teasing me.</font>

33:36.400 --> 33:38.480
<font color="#ffff00">Oh...</font>

33:38.520 --> 33:42.120
<font color="#ffff00">Ernst is always telling me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I am too serious.</font>

33:42.160 --> 33:45.160
And you always tell me
I am not serious enough.

33:45.200 --> 33:47.560
<font color="#ffff00">For a queen, perhaps.</font>

33:49.280 --> 33:51.280
But now, without your hat...

33:53.480 --> 33:55.720
..I think you're just right.

34:13.600 --> 34:15.840
(LEAVES CRUNCH AS ALBERT WALKS AWAY)

34:23.360 --> 34:26.080
<font color="#00ffff">Lord Alfred.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Did you return with the Queen?</font>

34:26.120 --> 34:28.960
<font color="#00ff00">No, I came back with Prince Ernest.</font>

34:29.520 --> 34:32.920
<font color="#00ff00">We were er...superfluous.</font>

34:33.920 --> 34:35.840
<font color="#00ffff">Ah.</font>

34:35.880 --> 34:38.159
Albert,
what happened to your mother?

34:40.080 --> 34:42.880
I only know that she died
when you were very young.

34:45.760 --> 34:49.960
<font color="#ffff00">She ran away from my father,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">just before my fifth birthday,</font>

34:50.000 --> 34:52.000
<font color="#ffff00">with her equerry.</font>

34:55.199 --> 34:56.960
<font color="#ffff00">She died a few years later.</font>

34:58.440 --> 35:00.640
<font color="#ffff00">I never saw her again.</font>

35:03.160 --> 35:04.920
(DOG BARKING)

35:04.960 --> 35:07.960
Sounds like Dash.
<font color="#ffff00">I'll find him.</font>

35:10.040 --> 35:11.480
Dash?

35:11.520 --> 35:13.640
(WHIMPERING)
<font color="#ffff00">ALBERT: Dash?</font>

35:13.680 --> 35:15.800
VICTORIA: Dash?

35:16.760 --> 35:18.120
<font color="#ffff00">No, no, no.</font>

35:19.200 --> 35:21.880
Is he hurt? Dash...
<font color="#ffff00">I think the leg is broken.</font>

35:22.840 --> 35:25.760
(DOG WHIMPERING)
Ssh. <font color="#ffff00">Hold him.</font>

35:30.800 --> 35:32.800
<font color="#ffff00">Hold him still.</font>

35:33.760 --> 35:35.200
<font color="#ffff00">Good boy.</font>

35:35.240 --> 35:37.240
<font color="#ffff00">Ah-ah-ah...</font>

35:37.280 --> 35:41.080
I know my attachment may seem
foolish, but... (SIGHS)

35:42.120 --> 35:45.560
..when I was living at Kensington,
Dash was my only real friend.

35:46.280 --> 35:48.280
<font color="#ffff00">And now it is different?</font>

35:49.680 --> 35:51.280
Yes.

35:52.680 --> 35:54.440
I have Lord Melbourne now and...

35:54.960 --> 35:56.960
..my ladies, of course.

35:59.160 --> 36:03.360
<font color="#ffff00">I wish you had not been so much with</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Melbourne. He is not serious.</font>

36:04.080 --> 36:06.400
He does not choose to appear serious.

36:07.160 --> 36:09.440
It is the English manner, but,
Albert...

36:10.440 --> 36:12.880
..he is a man of great feeling.

36:15.000 --> 36:17.000
<font color="#ffff00">Perhaps you should marry him.</font>

36:20.160 --> 36:21.240
Albert!

36:22.480 --> 36:25.240
<font color="#ffff00">Do you know the day when I was</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in the city? You know what I saw?</font>

36:25.280 --> 36:27.480
<font color="#ffff00">I saw a child,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">maybe four or five years old,</font>

36:27.520 --> 36:29.400
<font color="#ffff00">selling matches, one at a time.</font>

36:29.440 --> 36:32.040
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Melbourne chooses not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to look at that, but I must.</font>

36:32.920 --> 36:35.360
<font color="#ffff00">We cannot close our eyes</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to the world around us.</font>

36:35.400 --> 36:38.120
<font color="#ffff00">If you wish to surround yourself</font>
<font color="#ffff00">with sycophants, go ahead.</font>

36:38.160 --> 36:41.680
<font color="#ffff00">I, on the other hand, would rather</font>
<font color="#ffff00">see things for what they are.</font>

36:45.720 --> 36:48.320
How dare you? May I remind you that,

36:48.360 --> 36:52.160
while you were looking at paintings
in Italy, I was ruling this country?

36:52.200 --> 36:54.240
Yet you have been here a few days

36:54.280 --> 36:56.560
and you assume you know my people
better than I do.

36:56.600 --> 36:59.280
I do not need you
to tell me what to think, Albert.

37:01.120 --> 37:03.120
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

37:03.160 --> 37:05.160
<font color="#ffff00">That's Lord Melbourne's job.</font>

37:25.040 --> 37:27.040
(DOG WHINING SOFTLY)

37:28.840 --> 37:31.480
<font color="#00ff00">I find it hard to believe</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that she has said nothing to you.</font>

37:31.520 --> 37:33.520
<font color="#00ff00">Why, you were with her for hours.</font>

37:33.560 --> 37:35.400
<font color="#00ff00">Ernst would have taken her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to bed by now.</font>

37:35.440 --> 37:37.160
<font color="#ffff00">Enough!</font>

37:44.240 --> 37:46.480
<font color="#00ff00">DUCHESS:</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Albert and Ernest are leaving.</font>

37:46.520 --> 37:48.200
<font color="#00ffff">With no engagement.</font>

37:48.240 --> 37:50.240
He is not a British subject.

37:51.480 --> 37:53.480
I could not stop him,
even if I wanted to.

37:53.520 --> 37:56.720
<font color="#00ffff">Of course you can. You simply</font>
<font color="#00ffff">propose. </font><font color="#ffffff"> Oh, is that all?</font>

37:58.640 --> 38:01.080
I'm afraid, Uncle, it is not so easy.
<font color="#00ffff">But why not?</font>

38:01.120 --> 38:03.800
(EMOTIONALLY) Because
I'm not sure he will say yes.

38:03.840 --> 38:06.520
<font color="#00ffff">But at least you will know that,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">if he says yes,</font>

38:06.560 --> 38:08.560
<font color="#00ffff">it will be with his heart.</font>

38:09.320 --> 38:13.760
<font color="#00ffff">But you will never know,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">unless you ask him, Victoria.</font>

38:13.800 --> 38:17.200
<font color="#00ffff">You are being childish. You cannot</font>
<font color="#00ffff">leave because you had a squabble.</font>

38:17.240 --> 38:19.080
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria and I are not suited.</font>

38:19.120 --> 38:21.840
<font color="#ffff00">This marriage is convenient</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to everyone except us.</font>

38:21.880 --> 38:24.720
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, but you like her. I know you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">do, and she likes you, too.</font>

38:24.760 --> 38:26.840
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria likes many people, I think.</font>

38:27.680 --> 38:29.360
<font color="#ffff00">Lord Melbourne, for example.</font>

38:29.400 --> 38:31.880
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, he's old enough</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to be her father.</font>

38:33.240 --> 38:36.800
<font color="#00ffff">Where are you going now?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">To take a look at their Parliament.</font>

38:36.840 --> 38:39.760
<font color="#ffff00">That is one British institution</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I can admire.</font>

38:39.800 --> 38:41.400
<font color="#00ffff">Is something the matter, Ma'am?</font>

38:41.440 --> 38:44.080
Albert thinks
I'm too friendly with you.

38:46.760 --> 38:48.760
<font color="#00ffff">And what do you think?</font>

38:49.960 --> 38:51.960
I don't know.

38:55.240 --> 38:58.840
Albert always looks at me as if
I have done something wrong. I...

38:59.880 --> 39:01.880
I would like him to smile at me.

39:03.680 --> 39:05.760
<font color="#00ffff">Well, he does not smile very often.</font>

39:05.800 --> 39:07.320
I know!

39:07.360 --> 39:09.760
That's why I want him to smile at me.

39:12.040 --> 39:14.000
<font color="#00ffff">Well, if that is your intention,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am,</font>

39:14.040 --> 39:15.920
<font color="#00ffff">I don't see how he could resist.</font>

39:18.240 --> 39:20.240
Do you really believe so?

39:21.360 --> 39:22.960
(SIGHS)

39:25.280 --> 39:27.840
<font color="#00ffff">Only a fool would turn you away,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am.</font>

39:33.760 --> 39:37.040
<font color="#00ffff">SKERRETT: Do you want it done</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in any particular way, Ma'am?</font>

39:37.920 --> 39:40.000
You look different today.

39:40.040 --> 39:42.760
Oh, I know. You don't have a collar.

39:44.040 --> 39:46.040
<font color="#00ffff">I lost it, Ma'am.</font>

39:47.000 --> 39:49.840
Please...take one of mine.

39:49.880 --> 39:51.880
No, take several.

39:51.920 --> 39:55.080
<font color="#00ffff">I couldn't possibly...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">We must both look our best today.</font>

39:57.240 --> 39:59.280
Don't you think?

40:01.280 --> 40:03.280
(BABIES CRYING)

40:12.560 --> 40:14.680
<font color="#ffff00">Nanny!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Nancy.</font>

40:14.720 --> 40:16.200
<font color="#00ffff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

40:16.240 --> 40:18.240
<font color="#00ff00">I am glad to see you, Nancy.</font>

40:19.560 --> 40:21.560
<font color="#00ff00">And I'm sorry about before.</font>

40:22.400 --> 40:24.240
<font color="#00ffff">I know.</font>

40:24.280 --> 40:29.000
<font color="#00ff00">But sometimes...I think of you in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the Palace,</font>

40:29.040 --> 40:32.320
<font color="#00ff00">doing the Queen's hair the way</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I taught you, and I think...</font>

40:34.320 --> 40:36.040
<font color="#00ff00">.."That should have been my life."</font>

40:38.080 --> 40:40.200
<font color="#00ff00">Eliza Skerrett, the Queen's dresser.</font>

40:42.920 --> 40:44.920
<font color="#00ff00">But, instead, I'm nobody.</font>

40:45.640 --> 40:49.160
<font color="#00ffff">You could have given her up,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">found another job, but you didn't.</font>

40:49.760 --> 40:52.720
<font color="#00ff00">No. I wanted to keep her safe.</font>

40:54.640 --> 40:57.400
<font color="#00ffff">What we did, we did for her.</font>

41:02.880 --> 41:04.640
<font color="#ffff00">Mama!</font>

41:04.680 --> 41:06.800
<font color="#00ff00">(CHUCKLES)</font>

41:09.640 --> 41:12.240
<font color="#00ffff">I've brought you something.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, you didn't?</font>

41:12.280 --> 41:14.440
<font color="#00ffff">No. </font><font color="#00ff00"> (GASPS)</font>
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen gave them to me.</font>

41:15.400 --> 41:18.720
<font color="#00ff00">It's exquisite.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">The Queen must like you.</font>

41:20.440 --> 41:22.440
<font color="#00ffff">Like me? I don't know about that.</font>

41:23.440 --> 41:25.600
<font color="#00ffff">But sometimes she notices me...</font>

41:25.640 --> 41:28.880
<font color="#ffff00">Mummy.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">..when I'm doing her hair...</font>

41:28.920 --> 41:33.760
<font color="#00ffff">and she sees that we're just</font>
<font color="#00ffff">two girls, doing our best.</font>

41:35.760 --> 41:37.760
<font color="#00ff00">Doing our best.</font>

41:38.960 --> 41:41.000
<font color="#ffff00">Mama.</font>

41:41.040 --> 41:43.040
<font color="#00ff00">(CHUCKLES)</font>

41:49.720 --> 41:53.800
<font color="#00ffff">Your Serene Highnesses, allow me</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to welcome you to the House.</font>

41:53.840 --> 41:56.600
<font color="#ffff00">I've always wanted to see</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the place that banished tyranny.</font>

41:56.640 --> 41:58.880
<font color="#00ffff">Well, I do wish the Queen shared</font>
<font color="#00ffff">your feelings.</font>

41:58.920 --> 42:02.920
<font color="#00ffff">I fear she finds the unruliness</font>
<font color="#00ffff">distasteful.</font>

42:02.960 --> 42:05.080
<font color="#ffff00">I thought she followed you in</font>
<font color="#ffff00">everything.</font>

42:05.120 --> 42:07.280
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, well, once, perhaps.</font>

42:07.320 --> 42:11.240
<font color="#00ffff">Now she's settled into being Queen,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I find she ignores me more and more.</font>

42:15.680 --> 42:19.400
<font color="#00ffff">The fact is, my ministry will not</font>
<font color="#00ffff">last for ever.</font>

42:19.440 --> 42:22.120
(DISTANT RAISED VOICES)
<font color="#00ffff">Then I will return thankfully</font>

42:22.160 --> 42:23.680
<font color="#00ffff">to Brocket Hall.</font>

42:24.920 --> 42:28.000
<font color="#00ff00">That will be hard for the Queen,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I think.</font>

42:28.040 --> 42:29.720
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps.</font>

42:29.760 --> 42:32.840
<font color="#00ffff">But, in truth, I do think the time</font>
<font color="#00ffff">has come for me to retire.</font>

42:44.240 --> 42:47.720
It's so clever of you to find
gardenias. <font color="#00ffff">It wasn't easy, Ma'am.</font>

42:47.760 --> 42:52.960
Lord Melbourne grows them at Brocket
Hall, but...I could not ask him.

42:56.520 --> 42:58.120
<font color="#00ffff">There.</font>

42:58.840 --> 43:00.960
<font color="#00ffff">Are you happy with your choice,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Ma'am?</font>

43:35.040 --> 43:37.040
<font color="#ffff00">I was told you wanted to see me.</font>

43:38.000 --> 43:40.120
I want to ask you something.

43:40.720 --> 43:42.720
But before I do...

43:44.440 --> 43:46.880
..I must be sure
that you will not mind me asking.

43:46.920 --> 43:49.200
<font color="#ffff00">You're wearing those flowers again.</font>

44:07.320 --> 44:09.640
(Should I ask my question now?)

44:09.680 --> 44:11.800
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I wish you would.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

44:18.440 --> 44:20.040
Albert...

44:22.600 --> 44:24.600
..would you do me the honour of...

44:25.840 --> 44:28.560
Oh, no, that sounds wrong.

44:37.920 --> 44:39.520
Albert...

44:42.840 --> 44:45.080
..will you marry me?

44:51.320 --> 44:52.920
<font color="#ffff00">That depends.</font>

44:54.760 --> 44:57.040
On what?

44:57.080 --> 44:59.720
<font color="#ffff00">(On if you'll let me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">kiss you first.)</font>

45:03.040 --> 45:05.680
If I do, will you say yes?
<font color="#ffff00">I have to kiss you.</font>

45:07.880 --> 45:09.880
(CHUCKLES)

45:10.880 --> 45:13.520
(LAUGHS)

45:22.760 --> 45:25.320
<font color="#ffff00">For me, this is not</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a marriage of convenience.</font>

45:26.880 --> 45:28.480
No.

45:30.360 --> 45:32.960
I think it will be
a marriage of inconvenience.

45:35.280 --> 45:37.200
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

45:40.000 --> 45:42.000
(But I have no choice.)

45:44.520 --> 45:46.520
<font color="#ffff00">Neither do I.</font>

46:09.760 --> 46:11.800
We must get married
as soon as possible.

46:11.840 --> 46:14.680
<font color="#00ffff">This is the moment to settle</font>
<font color="#00ffff">your title and allowance.</font>

46:14.720 --> 46:17.080
I told Albert I would settle this.
How can I explain?

46:17.120 --> 46:20.360
<font color="#ffff00">I want to be her husband,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but I cannot be like Dash,</font>

46:20.400 --> 46:22.320
<font color="#ffff00">waiting for her to throw me a treat.</font>

46:22.360 --> 46:24.360
Why does the allowance
mean so much to you?

46:24.400 --> 46:26.040
Is it
so that you can keep a mistress?

46:26.080 --> 46:28.520
<font color="#00ffff">Spend an hour in the company</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of Gretchen here.</font>

46:28.560 --> 46:30.840
I think I would like
my wedding dress to be white.

46:30.880 --> 46:33.680
<font color="#00ffff">How can we be sure Prince Albert</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is a Protestant?</font>

46:33.720 --> 46:37.600
<font color="#00ff00">We cannot have Germans</font>
<font color="#00ff00">running the country!</font>

